As of the [[census]]<ref name="GR2">{{cite web|url=https://www.census.gov|publisher=[[United States Census Bureau]]|accessdate=2008-01-31|title=U.S. Census website}}</ref> of 2000, there were 423 people, 158 households, and 127 families residing in the city. By the [[2020 United States census|2020 census]], its population was 402.

